testSteps.description: When i search for an employee using the header search bar: Mahmoud Agig Abdelrahim
When i go to biographical info
Then the edit property of biographical info fields for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to personal info
Then the edit property of personal info fields for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to national ID
Then the edit property of national ID fields for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to contact info
Then the edit property of email info for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to contact info
Then the edit property of phone info for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to address
Then the edit property of address for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to contact info
Then the edit property of emergency contact info for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to employment details
Then the edit property of employment details for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to work eligibility
Then the edit property of work eligibility for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to job relationship
Then the edit property of job relationship for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to job info
Then the edit property of job info for res HR CA should be correctly set: 10/05/2024
When i go to non recurring pay elements
Then the edit property of non recurring pay elements for res HR CA should be correctly set
When i go to compensation info
Then the edit property of compensation info for res HR CA should be correctly set: 10/05/2024
